Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Oprezno* kroči po snegu da ne padneš. (*Carefully* step on the snow so you don't fall.) 
2. Molim te, vozi *oprezno* jer ima mnogo leda na putu. (Please drive *carefully* because there's a lot of ice on the road.)
3. Moramo biti *oprezni* prilikom izbora novih saradnika. (We need to be *cautious* when choosing new colleagues.)
4. *Oprezno* otvori prozor da ne pukne staklo. (*Gently* open the window so the glass doesn't break.)
5. Ako primetiš bilo kakve sumnjive aktivnosti, odmah *oprezno* pozovi policiju. (If you notice any suspicious activities, immediately *prudently* call the police.)
6. Njegova politika je uvek bila da se ide *oprezno* i da se ne donose nagli zaključci. (His policy has always been to proceed *cautiously* and not to jump to conclusions.)
7. *Opreznošću* je spasila svoj život u saobraćajnoj nesreći. (She saved her life in a car accident through *caution*.) 
8. *Opreznost* je majka mudrosti. (*Caution* is the mother of wisdom.)
9. U ovakvoj situaciji moramo pokazati *opreznost* i strpljenje. (In this situation, we must show *prudence* and patience.)
10. Predlažem da *oprezno* razmotrimo sve opcije pre nego što donesemo odluku. (I suggest that we *carefully* consider all the options before making a decision.)